---
import ContactForm from '@components/ContactForm.astro'
import Grid from '@components/Grid.astro'
import Layout from '@layouts/Layout.astro'

import CaseStudySectionText from '@components/case-studies/case-study/CaseStudySectionText.astro'
import CaseStudyResults from '@components/case-studies/case-study/CaseStudyResults.astro'
import CaseStudyHeader from '@components/case-studies/case-study/CaseStudyHeader.astro'
import CaseStudyToggleButton from '@components/case-studies/case-study/CaseStudyToggleButton.astro'
import CaseStudyMetaData from '@components/case-studies/case-study/CaseStudyMetaData.astro'
import CaseStudyShout from '@components/case-studies/case-study/CaseStudyShout.astro'
import CaseStudyNav from '@components/case-studies/case-study/CaseStudyNav.astro'
import CaseStudyImages from '@components/case-studies/case-study/CaseStudyImages.astro'
import { getCaseStudyNav } from '@data/caseStudies'

import hero from '@assets/case-studies/farmers-union/hero.webp'
import squareOne from '@assets/case-studies/farmers-union/squareOne.svg'
import squareTwo from '@assets/case-studies/farmers-union/squareTwo.webp'
import wideOne from '@assets/case-studies/farmers-union/wideOne.webp'
import wideTwo from '@assets/case-studies/farmers-union/wideTwo.webp'

const { previous, next } = getCaseStudyNav('farmers')
---

<Layout
  title="Farmers Union Greek Style Yogurt Case Study"
  description="Website design and development for Farmers Union Greek Yogurt, a Bega Group dairy brand sold across major Australian supermarkets, in the consumer packaged goods sector. Pixel Agency translated the brand's updated packaging into a cohesive web and mobile experience, lifting traffic on launch."
>
  <article id="case-study-page">
    <CaseStudyHeader>
      <span slot="title">Farmers Union Greek Style Yogurt</span>
      <span slot="industry">Food & Beverage</span>
      <span slot="services">Design, Development</span>
      <span slot="duration">2 months</span>
    </CaseStudyHeader>

    <CaseStudyToggleButton />

    <!-- Single shell: all images + summary (left pane) / all case study text (right pane) -->
    <section class="pb-12 lg:pb-18">
      <Grid>
        <div id="case-study-shell" class="case-study-shell col-span-full">
          <div class="case-study-left-pane min-w-0 overflow-hidden">
            <CaseStudyImages
              heroImage={{ src: hero }}
              summary="How Pixel Agency translated Farmers Union Greek Yogurt's updated packaging brand into a cohesive digital experience, sharpening the visual language for screens and lifting site traffic on launch."
              squareImages={[{ src: squareOne }, { src: squareTwo }]}
              wideImages={[{ src: wideOne }, { src: wideTwo }]}
            />
          </div>

          <div class="case-study-right-pane min-w-0">
            <CaseStudyShout>Bringing a refreshed yogurt brand to life across web and mobile.</CaseStudyShout>

            <CaseStudySectionText title="The client" noTopMargin={true}>
              <p class="">
                Farmers Union Greek Yogurt is one of the dairy brands in the Bega Group portfolio, sold across all the
                major Australian supermarkets. Their products sit on shelves alongside the country's most recognisable
                dairy names, competing for attention in a category where packaging and presentation do a lot of the
                heavy lifting.
              </p>
            </CaseStudySectionText>

            <CaseStudySectionText title="The problem" textColour="text-pixel-red">
              <p>
                Farmers Union had refreshed its packaging brand, sharpening the look on shelf and giving the range a
                clearer, more confident identity. The challenge was getting that same brand to land on the web.
                Packaging and digital are different beasts. Colours that pop on a tub under supermarket lighting don't
                always translate to a screen, and visual choices that work at arm's length need rethinking when they're
                being viewed on a phone in someone's hand. Without the right adaptation, the new brand risked feeling
                inconsistent across touchpoints, undoing the cohesion the rebrand was meant to achieve.
              </p>
            </CaseStudySectionText>

            <CaseStudySectionText title="The approach" textColour="text-pixel-orange">
              <p>
                Bega brought us in based on the working relationship we've built across most of their major brands. We
                started by getting properly across the new packaging direction, sitting with the design language and
                understanding what made it work in the physical world before deciding how to translate it. Discovery
                here wasn't about finding the brand, it was about pressure-testing how it would behave in a different
                medium and where it would need adjustment to keep its impact.
              </p>
            </CaseStudySectionText>

            <CaseStudySectionText title="The solution" textColour="text-pixel-green">
              <p>
                From there, we moved into design and development, rebuilding the digital presence around the refreshed
                brand. The work covered the detail that determines whether a brand feels right on screen: colour
                corrections to make the palette read cleanly on digital displays, spacing and layout choices tuned for
                web and mobile, and messaging and calls to action reshaped to fit how people actually move through a
                website. The output was a digital experience that felt unmistakably Farmers Union, in step with the new
                packaging rather than a watered-down version of it.
              </p>
            </CaseStudySectionText>

            <CaseStudySectionText title="The results" textColour="text-pixel-blue">
              <p>
                The relaunch landed well, and the brand sat right alongside the rest of the Bega portfolio in look and
                feel:
              </p>
              <CaseStudyResults
                results={[
                  {
                    title: 'A clear lift',
                    description: 'in website traffic following the new brand release',
                    backgroundColour: '#e8c42f'
                  },
                  {
                    title: 'Visual cohesion',
                    description: 'across packaging, web, and mobile',
                    backgroundColour: '#6498c9'
                  },
                  {
                    title: 'A digital presence',
                    description: 'that matches the confidence of the refreshed shelf identity',
                    backgroundColour: '#F37992'
                  }
                ]}
              />

              <div class="mt-6 lg:mt-12"></div>
              <CaseStudyShout
                >Brand work that holds together across packaging and digital is harder than it looks, and the difference
                shows when it's done right.</CaseStudyShout
              >
            </CaseStudySectionText>

            <CaseStudyMetaData
              client={{ name: 'Farmers Union Greek Style Yogurt', url: 'https://farmersunionyogurt.com.au/' }}
              industry={['Food & Beverage']}
              serviceNames={['Design', 'Development']}
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </Grid>
    </section>

    {/* Navigation section */}
    <CaseStudyNav previousCaseStudy={previous} nextCaseStudy={next} />

    <ContactForm title="Discuss a similar challenge" displayDescription={false} />
  </article>

  <style>
    #case-study-page {
      --case-study-border: color-mix(in oklab, var(--color-black) 8%, transparent);
      --case-study-placeholder: #d9d9d9;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1023px) {
      .case-study-shell {
        display: flex;
        gap: 0;
        overflow: clip;
      }

      .case-study-left-pane {
        flex: 0 0 auto;
        width: 100%;
        max-height: 5000px;
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateX(0);
        transition:
          width 420ms cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1),
          max-height 420ms cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1),
          opacity 240ms ease,
          transform 420ms cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1);
        will-change: width, max-height, opacity, transform;
      }

      #case-study-page[data-panel-state='open'] .case-study-left-pane {
        width: 0;
        max-height: 0;
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateX(-2rem);
        pointer-events: none;
      }

      .case-study-right-pane {
        flex: 0 0 auto;
        width: 0;
        max-height: 0;
        opacity: 0;
        overflow: clip;
        transform: translateX(2rem);
        transition:
          width 420ms cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1),
          max-height 420ms cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1),
          opacity 260ms ease,
          transform 420ms cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1);
        will-change: width, max-height, opacity, transform;
      }

      #case-study-page[data-panel-state='open'] .case-study-right-pane {
        width: 100%;
        max-height: 5000px;
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateX(0);
        pointer-events: auto;
      }
    }

    @media (min-width: 1024px) {
      .case-study-shell {
        display: flex;
        gap: 0;
        transition: gap 420ms cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1);
      }

      #case-study-page[data-panel-state='open'] .case-study-shell {
        gap: 1.25rem;
      }

      .case-study-left-pane,
      .case-study-right-pane {
        flex: 0 0 auto;
        transition:
          width 420ms cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1),
          max-height 420ms cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1),
          opacity 260ms ease,
          transform 420ms cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1);
        will-change: width, max-height, opacity, transform;
      }

      .case-study-left-pane {
        width: 100%;
        max-height: 5000px;
      }

      .case-study-right-pane {
        width: 0;
        max-height: 0;
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateX(2rem);
        overflow: clip;
        pointer-events: none;
      }

      #case-study-page[data-panel-state='open'] .case-study-left-pane {
        width: calc(50% - 0.625rem);
      }

      #case-study-page[data-panel-state='open'] .case-study-right-pane {
        width: calc(50% - 0.625rem);
        max-height: 5000px;
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateX(0);
        pointer-events: auto;
      }
    }

    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
      .case-study-shell,
      .case-study-left-pane,
      .case-study-right-pane {
        transition: none;
      }
    }
  </style>

  <script>
    function initCaseStudyPage() {
      const page = document.getElementById('case-study-page')
      const toggle = document.getElementById('case-study-toggle')
      if (!(page instanceof HTMLElement) || !(toggle instanceof HTMLButtonElement)) return
      const pageElement = page
      const toggleButton = toggle

      const mobileMedia = window.matchMedia('(max-width: 1023px)')

      function setToggleTextColor() {
        const accent = getComputedStyle(document.documentElement).getPropertyValue('--accent-bgc').trim()
        const match = accent.match(/(\d+)\s*,\s*(\d+)\s*,\s*(\d+)/)
        if (!match) return

        let red = parseInt(match[1], 10) / 255
        let green = parseInt(match[2], 10) / 255
        let blue = parseInt(match[3], 10) / 255

        red = red <= 0.03928 ? red / 12.92 : Math.pow((red + 0.055) / 1.055, 2.4)
        green = green <= 0.03928 ? green / 12.92 : Math.pow((green + 0.055) / 1.055, 2.4)
        blue = blue <= 0.03928 ? blue / 12.92 : Math.pow((blue + 0.055) / 1.055, 2.4)

        const luminance = 0.2126 * red + 0.7152 * green + 0.0722 * blue
        document.documentElement.style.setProperty('--case-study-toggle-text', luminance > 0.4 ? '#000' : '#fff')
      }

      function getDefaultState() {
        return 'closed'
      }

      if (!pageElement.dataset.panelState) {
        pageElement.dataset.panelState = getDefaultState()
      }

      function syncA11y() {
        const isOpen = pageElement.dataset.panelState === 'open'
        toggleButton.setAttribute('aria-expanded', String(isOpen))
      }

      setToggleTextColor()
      syncA11y()

      toggleButton.addEventListener('click', () => {
        pageElement.dataset.panelState = pageElement.dataset.panelState === 'open' ? 'closed' : 'open'
        syncA11y()
      })
    }

    initCaseStudyPage()
    document.addEventListener('astro:after-swap', initCaseStudyPage)
  </script>
</Layout>
